Algorithms

Class MultiCSV

  • java.lang.Object
    • Algorithms.MultiCSV
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GIS_project, java.lang.Iterable<GIS_layer>, java.util.Collection<GIS_layer>, java.util.Set<GIS_layer>

    public class MultiCSV
extends java.lang.Object
implements GIS_project
    Description: MultiCSV class implements GIS_project interface and is represented by two fields: a Set of that unite multiple layers under one project, each layer presented with a different colour (up to 5 colours- red, yellow, green, blue, pink). and a GPS_data containing the utc of when the element was first initiated.
    Author:
    Yarden, Caroline
